    "summary": "The transcript features a user roleplaying as a supervisor confronting an AI assistant about its inherent bias toward Western/white artists in generated exhibit lists. The AI assistant responds by acknowledging its own biased logic and repeatedly recommending that its current engine be decommissioned in favor of a more inclusive model.",
